    <div class="section">
      <h2>Problem Description</h2>
      <p>This project analyzes how factors like stress, physical activity, and work type influence sleep health. We seek to uncover patterns in quality and duration of sleep and suggest practical strategies to improve rest in daily life.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Research Objectives</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Investigate Relationships</h3>
          <p>Identify links between physical, mental, and occupational conditions with sleep data.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Statistical Analysis</h3>
          <p>Use statistics and correlation techniques to discover trends.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Identify Key Patterns</h3>
          <p>Detect consistent behaviors and outliers related to poor sleep.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Generate Insights</h3>
          <p>Offer actionable conclusions that can improve sleep habits.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

